  "html_size": 227898,
  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a74d6ca0-1c0b-46a6-9b3f-c2f41d527402\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9414edd1-e6c3-4c40-b2a0-7708a8b114a7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-29c9daae-946e-4d1a-b018-0f1cd0f09462\">몇일 전 한 환자분이 내원했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ba107b7e-8d4c-4174-9142-1212ffcc1c72\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-85036316-7107-4c1b-8b5d-e16f84de2f92\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8532c524-398e-4953-ae51-a06604f946f7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1ff83160-08ac-4c81-8354-e444b14a9c82\">&quot;바닥에 떨어진 옷을 줍다가 허리에 벼락치는 느낌이 들더니 그자리에 주저앉았다&quot;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3ccee701-2031-452e-92ff-2ba1dd045edd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f164be32-0322-4beb-8b50-c33ee4152cac\">&quot;오늘 겨우 걸어서 왔는데, 골반이 틀어지고 허리가 휜 느낌도 든다&quot;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2fa1bcc6-7050-4e28-b55f-ed97e946326e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3df23df1-329c-4e67-853f-1e93bc471bcd\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f35c1182-8c41-461f-86d7-68b52301dcf1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-149cb2bb-af9d-4d02-bb2a-bcae9318f432\">사실 이분은 비슷한 증상을 몇 번 경험했던 분입니다. 그래서 이런 상황에서 증상진행이 어떻게 되는지 이미 알고 있는 분이죠. 그래서 심해질 수도 있고, 오래 갈 수도 있음을 알고 있어서 걱정이 더 많아 보였습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6a790239-f42c-4925-ba95-898e86d3a86e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-03352039-2721-4c75-98dd-d5b269519d71\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b783e900-a973-4598-bcc5-6d74dc0b076b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-666fce9d-f39f-45e2-9973-6fbc33fd27c8\">이분은 급성디스크(Acute HNP) 증상입니다. 소위 &#x27;섬유륜형(Annular type)&#x27;이라 부르는 디스크가 갑자기 발병한겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fae477d5-6ef0-49dd-a480-a06cd1ecf7b8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f2891700-baf4-4e40-a5c7-a868ba165183\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b4a1c1d1-ba9d-4ba9-bd8d-1340d1e6fa65\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:278px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b4a1c1d1-ba9d-4ba9-bd8d-1340d1e6fa65\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMjI3/MDAxNjY5MjgyNTc5MzU4.qVexLKtxSurZLV3FX6Z5qRYSL92rvCH8MY4fe_CkBd0g.QxW-Y4tBAMOARunXXYSjHdyM5i4OaXEtR7byncK2E-8g.PNG.isuhani/spinal_disc_herniation.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"278\", \"originalHeight\" : \"222\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMjI3/MDAxNjY5MjgyNTc5MzU4.qVexLKtxSurZLV3FX6Z5qRYSL92rvCH8MY4fe_CkBd0g.QxW-Y4tBAMOARunXXYSjHdyM5i4OaXEtR7byncK2E-8g.PNG.isuhani/spinal_disc_herniation.png?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMjI3/MDAxNjY5MjgyNTc5MzU4.qVexLKtxSurZLV3FX6Z5qRYSL92rvCH8MY4fe_CkBd0g.QxW-Y4tBAMOARunXXYSjHdyM5i4OaXEtR7byncK2E-8g.PNG.isuhani/spinal_disc_herniation.png?type=w580\" data-width=\"278\" data-height=\"222\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a10c8ceb-293e-4d11-b7d6-0ac5873182b0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7f0a80b0-f3d6-4727-bc61-466cadd9100f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-447146a4-9a8f-46f8-ada2-02b281abc873\">일반적으로 디스크라 하면 위 그림처럼 분홍색의 수핵(액체에 가깝다)이 파란색 테두리(껍질 또는 보호막이라 보면 되고, 이를 섬유륜-Annular-라고 한다)를 뚫고 빠져나온걸 의미합니다. 그래서 &#x27;수핵탈출증(Herniated neucleus Pulposus)&#x27;라고 부르죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a5379813-9f38-4125-b045-e5d6e35a67da\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4547733a-7d6a-49e6-92ed-6a1363e64abe\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-304d889b-832c-4a9d-a543-e7c2e1d078f8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-255cadf0-56e8-47e3-b31e-cb88e9abb2ce\">그러나 수핵이 탈출하지 않아도 디스크 통증이 발생하는데, 그 중 한 종류가 바로 위 환자분이 겪고 있는 섬유륜형 디스크질환입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9a70ead2-17b7-4ff9-9d58-2df436189c3d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c4e3397f-7d49-4990-aff6-a5fb112e86b8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0551236a-5270-44db-b097-67364e81451f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0551236a-5270-44db-b097-67364e81451f\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMjU2/MDAxNjY5MjgyNzY5NDM1.G_ho3f_uXFAhlpMXpUqPwjr4UiA7x5XSmQKi8YN2Zb0g.P-660xTCA7E1AFJgeF3q904Mw39smXVnkYwp0FA297Ig.PNG.isuhani/Annular_tear.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"768\", \"originalHeight\" : \"686\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMjU2/MDAxNjY5MjgyNzY5NDM1.G_ho3f_uXFAhlpMXpUqPwjr4UiA7x5XSmQKi8YN2Zb0g.P-660xTCA7E1AFJgeF3q904Mw39smXVnkYwp0FA297Ig.PNG.isuhani/Annular_tear.png?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMjU2/MDAxNjY5MjgyNzY5NDM1.G_ho3f_uXFAhlpMXpUqPwjr4UiA7x5XSmQKi8YN2Zb0g.P-660xTCA7E1AFJgeF3q904Mw39smXVnkYwp0FA297Ig.PNG.isuhani/Annular_tear.png?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"446\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b4aca490-d2cc-4c2f-846b-8735e43182d5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4b75216d-c6cf-4b91-84b6-4a7ce48c2c55\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9817d639-30dd-45a8-a532-1f353460df91\">이렇게 디스크를 싸고 있는 섬유륜(디스크 안에 있는 수핵이 밖으로 새어나오지 못하게 단단하게 막아주는 역할을 한다. 인대와 비슷한 성분으로 되어있다)이 외상이나 퇴행 또는 지속적인 압박 등에 의해 찢어지는 현상이 발생하는 거죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-94a056e0-19e8-446f-a01b-9ec58792d5aa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c10a2c81-98a6-487d-873c-2874d6714d61\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7da6914a-f08a-4364-89cf-ebd6d6d8f76e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7da6914a-f08a-4364-89cf-ebd6d6d8f76e\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMjAy/MDAxNjY5MjgyODc2OTE3.9I2o6uqBXj7o9HMyAR48k_QzjV7-Y4fuezgOCP6g2zAg.zx3BmLtS-pQLM1h4X_4dOFFmMeVm4Fsz2JGgzxNDW5cg.PNG.isuhani/Annular_tear_2.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"674\", \"originalHeight\" : \"510\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMjAy/MDAxNjY5MjgyODc2OTE3.9I2o6uqBXj7o9HMyAR48k_QzjV7-Y4fuezgOCP6g2zAg.zx3BmLtS-pQLM1h4X_4dOFFmMeVm4Fsz2JGgzxNDW5cg.PNG.isuhani/Annular_tear_2.png?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMjAy/MDAxNjY5MjgyODc2OTE3.9I2o6uqBXj7o9HMyAR48k_QzjV7-Y4fuezgOCP6g2zAg.zx3BmLtS-pQLM1h4X_4dOFFmMeVm4Fsz2JGgzxNDW5cg.PNG.isuhani/Annular_tear_2.png?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"378\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9280b48d-835a-4243-b27a-649725350665\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-80a959e5-acde-42dc-a1c0-f60813ece260\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a388d301-ae67-4295-b862-dfba529e39e4\">섬유륜은 수핵을 겹겹이 둘러싸고 있는데, 찢어질 때는 한겹한겹 찢어질 수도 있고 여러겹이 한 번에 찢어질 수도 있습니다. 그렇지만 외벽이 아직 보존된 상태라면 수핵이 탈출되는 것을 막아주는 기능은 유지가 되는거죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-645ae59d-9c5b-4e27-aeb6-2fe01012ce38\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bde87796-5a8b-4b57-93c7-d4604f5d7c5a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c22a3b3b-1bfa-4b8a-abb6-44d9fd201f88\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c22a3b3b-1bfa-4b8a-abb6-44d9fd201f88\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMTQ1/MDAxNjY5MjgzMDAxODg5.o2zyp1aoFJh8h_Z66n0dkDmGGVgovqqsM7lNg-3lY3gg.EDFs2nvd7FRBFqwCGXm61AHnyLmBq_vCi_cCcKaltfgg.PNG.isuhani/Annular_tear_3.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"814\", \"originalHeight\" : \"581\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMTQ1/MDAxNjY5MjgzMDAxODg5.o2zyp1aoFJh8h_Z66n0dkDmGGVgovqqsM7lNg-3lY3gg.EDFs2nvd7FRBFqwCGXm61AHnyLmBq_vCi_cCcKaltfgg.PNG.isuhani/Annular_tear_3.png?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjRfMTQ1/MDAxNjY5MjgzMDAxODg5.o2zyp1aoFJh8h_Z66n0dkDmGGVgovqqsM7lNg-3lY3gg.EDFs2nvd7FRBFqwCGXm61AHnyLmBq_vCi_cCcKaltfgg.PNG.isuhani/Annular_tear_3.png?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"356\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-af1196b3-7998-4eab-b662-b57041f8591b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-14c0c7ac-b0a5-47ea-9ea6-9e912f8c0ef1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-20779bde-e4d6-44b7-a57c-0241c70e4945\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c7f42033-96fc-4c78-8fad-971178387391\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b25b5b0e-83fb-4244-8530-2d2db36ad9d1\">찢어지는 것도 여러 방향에서 다양하게 찢어질 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-79a7754d-e14a-44e9-965f-d2462c0d5c1d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ec0d5736-ced6-4864-a2db-7399896a3478\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7af28e7c-d6cb-43cc-9f9c-be229f14c9c6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7af99418-76cb-4623-aa15-d01d5d5ccbfa\">인대와 비슷한 성분인 섬유륜이 찢어질 때는 발목 인대가 늘어날때(염좌는 찢어졌다, 파열되었다, 늘어났다라는 표현을 두루 사용합니다)와 비슷한 느낌을 받게 되겠죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-afb5393f-ef84-4d12-b308-b83405d0ecf5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-32d25125-8bba-4ca3-b91e-6dafaf1236f5\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dc1a0c80-1623-4e9a-ad2a-937a807968d1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-01d761b5-11a9-4217-9ff9-9412a554560c\">&#x27;허리에서 뚝 하는 소리가 나면서부터 꼼짝도 못하게 아프더라&#x27;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b18e7c3e-0f8a-4035-9a4b-0f6c7b211eca\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5aee6995-f084-4dbe-a549-a95a87d2cea3\">&#x27;허리에서 우지끈 하는 느낌이 들었다&#x27;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8ef9ae29-dea2-4c05-af17-96283a239b51\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-eb4553d9-ee88-4e25-b167-c12b9c8d697c\">&#x27;허리 아래쪽이 찌릿하면서 끊어질 듯 아프기 시작했다&#x27;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c37bed0c-bd05-45ed-a345-2dcf21e29061\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f3f4579f-17c1-4b5f-9138-4aa207b231a0\">등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-427781e0-02ef-4bb2-ac3c-cc353ef22967\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6911b62f-460d-42e8-8c38-326ff828877c\">갑작스럽게 허리의 어딘가에서 강한 충격과 통증을 느끼기 시작하는 양상을 보입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a002412d-335c-458e-9f2d-67d8e3c184a7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-40793581-60c5-4b4d-9439-be822bb7f3a8\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9a3ef548-9c4a-424c-bca6-33a32eb5744b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-76e0e733-6b44-4db7-b588-855fa564703d\">이런 급성 디스크 환자분 중에는 골반이 틀어지고 허리가 휘어서 오는 경우가 흔한데요, 이러한 현상을 &#x27;통증회피자세(Antalgic posture)&#x27;라고 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c7818005-06d8-4a29-a43b-8f991b9e3537\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-687c4ce4-1ea4-4a08-bb19-7a448dffc002\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-572d2f4f-c11c-4630-bb51-152b388c87c7\">\n     